{"tid":2200991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白俄羅斯示威持續  最少46人被捕  集會開始即拘捕","createTime":"2020-09-13T12:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T14:48:40.000Z","uid":227801,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5959f92fe9a8491a49e5e6148e0e291e0267fd00","tid":2200991,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=405353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405353&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513ezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=9dd55744\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405353&h=2b7a6cba\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=405353</a><br />\n10小時前&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】白俄羅斯的反政府示威持續，警方採取行動，最少46人被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n在首都明斯克，大約一萬名婦女在市中心聚集，要求總統盧卡申科下台，以及釋放反對派領袖科列斯尼科娃。<br />\n<br />\n當局被指企圖強迫科列斯尼科娃，出境不成功後將她扣押。有人權組織表示，警方在示威活動開始後不久，就採取拘捕行動，已流亡立陶宛的另一名反對派領袖季哈諾夫斯卡婭，要求警方停止打壓異見人士，又指他們對婦女使用暴力可恥。<br />\n<br />\n面對國際壓力一直表現強硬的盧卡申科，與國防官員舉行會議。他表示若北約軍隊，在荷蘭及立陶宛的軍演結束後<br />\n<br />\n仍然不撤離，白俄將有所行動。盧卡申科周一，將會前往俄羅斯與總統普京會面，是白俄局勢出現不穩後，兩人首次面對面舉行會談。"},{"pid":"c8850a1f5d96f4c6d3cdb29394f398d4da10e0fa","tid":2200991,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514cc142fd544e78a9bef8c083c3bd3613a28e8b","tid":2200991,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ac83894bf857cb9f611a5377cf9fe78bc8cf3b","tid":2200991,"uid":155784,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"香港黑警向世界展示獨裁政權做法"},{"pid":"ee1a401662ffe51fb2b33421a70f56f8a6be21fc","tid":2200991,"uid":289292,"like":2,"di